reviews.text: Great place for dinner, nice food, good service.  Just note they have a chef from five star hotel.  Reasonable pricing
Quite nice place and food

Possibly near the upper end considering its district, but the quality , service and ambience definitely compensate as well as justified such price. 

For reference: my choice of Valentine's set for two consists of two starters, soups, entrees and one dessert. It costs around HKD550 (service charge included) in total.
nice atmosphere with fine food
Best salad ever... cannot fault it.  Just needs more patrons.  A word of warning, after 21:00 it is too late as the chef packs up.
